  "detailed_description": "In regular combat (shield mode), you can use a magic ball to break through the skills launched by enemies, or draw your own magic ball launch trajectory to break through more skills launched by enemies, thereby reducing the damage suffered by friendly shields. With this feature, you can even challenge a much stronger boss to obtain high reward rewards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/6429ec94034ec6e7b791cf977fb06ec8.poster.avif?t=1715012059\" width=540 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/6429ec94034ec6e7b791cf977fb06ec8.webm?t=1715012059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/6429ec94034ec6e7b791cf977fb06ec8.mp4?t=1715012059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/dd907ac8db93b8091bf6f68e4fc2769e.poster.avif?t=1715012059\" width=540 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/dd907ac8db93b8091bf6f68e4fc2769e.webm?t=1715012059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/dd907ac8db93b8091bf6f68e4fc2769e.mp4?t=1715012059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In the duel mode, make use of the characteristics of friendly forces to defeat opponents that are difficult to defeat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/58066fe28764e208dec577c605bd7aa8.poster.avif?t=1715012059\" width=540 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/58066fe28764e208dec577c605bd7aa8.webm?t=1715012059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913260/extras/58066fe28764e208dec577c605bd7aa8.mp4?t=1715012059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Exploring the Secret Realm<br>Random exploration of the secret realm can bring some random experiences, both good and bad, and the difficulty will increase layer by layer. At this point, it is necessary to make good use of one's own material resources and enhance the blessings during exploration.<br><br>It's quite interesting to have a good showdown with your own level opponents in the desert arena.<br><br>Double Demon Kings and Three Demon Kings Challenge, increasing the challenge of the game. There are other challenges and so on, waiting for you to discover.",
